commit.message:
Enable `symbolize_keys: true` for inline tables

Keys in a inline table have not been symbolized even when
`symbolize_keys: true` since 26ade435d64cef1ba0ecb8cd5eaf65afe811a104.
This commit fixes it and adds the test case.
